    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《杳之境》是一款敘事導向的2D像素遊戲。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >爆肝工程師林宗達為了拯救昏迷多年的阿媽，意外闖入光怪陸離的妖怪世界中。<strong> </strong><br> <br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125880/extras/779b4a439be7d77b39e2640bc08fda3c.poster.avif?t=1765946036\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125880/extras/779b4a439be7d77b39e2640bc08fda3c.webm?t=1765946036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125880/extras/779b4a439be7d77b39e2640bc08fda3c.mp4?t=1765946036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>「等等… 阿媽妳怎麼變成手機了？」</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>結識古靈精怪的鬼怪居民們，化解一樁樁荒謬離奇的事件。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一起踏上這笑中帶淚的歸途吧！</strong>  </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>遊戲特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >獨特的東方像素美術。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >巨量可愛小妖怪藏在杳之境的各個角落，等你來發現。（並把牠們收錄進圖鑑內！）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125880/extras/e989a7ce9ae6a755613c591a4821b206.poster.avif?t=1765946036\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125880/extras/e989a7ce9ae6a755613c591a4821b206.webm?t=1765946036\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3125880/extras/e989a7ce9ae6a755613c591a4821b206.mp4?t=1765946036\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有貓。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >妖怪們搞出了好多奇怪事件，或許你可以參一咖。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >宗達與阿媽的祖孫探索之旅。</p></li></ul>",
